# Guild Member List View Implementation

Add a "Member List" column to the Guild Management table to allow operators to view the members of a specific guild.

## Proposed Changes

### Types & API

#### [MODIFY] [guild.ts](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%B0/src/types/guild.ts)
Add `GuildMember` interface:
- `player_id`: string
- `username`: string
- `rank`: 'LEADER' | 'ELDER' | 'MEMBER'
- `join_time`: string
- `total_contribution`: number
- `last_active`: string

#### [MODIFY] [guild.ts](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%B0/src/api/guild.ts)
