## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate to "玩家管理 > 公會設定".
2. Scroll to any guild in the list.
3. Click "成員名單" in the actions column.
4. Verify that a modal opens displaying the member list correctly.
5. Click a player ID in the member list to verify navigation to player details.
